<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About Us - Feedback/Complaint Form</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../static/css/abtstyle.css">
    <!-- Add FontAwesome for the icons -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/5.15.3/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>

    <div class="about-section">
        <h2>About Us</h2>
        <p>Welcome to Bite-A-Way! We are dedicated to providing the best dining experience with a variety of cuisines from around the world. We value your feedback and are always striving to improve. Please fill out the form below to share your thoughts with us!</p>
    </div>

    <div class="form-section">
        <h3 class="section-title"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i> Feedback / Complaint Form</h3>
        
        <form action="/submit-feedback" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            <div class="form-row">
                <div class="form-group form-group-large">
                    <label for="name">Your Name *</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" class="form-control" required>
                </div>
                
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email Address *</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" class="form-control" required>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="message">Your Message *</label>
                <textarea id="message" name="message" class="form-control" rows="4" required></textarea>
                <small>Let us know your thoughts, feedback, or any complaints you may have.</small>
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="rating">Rating (1 to 5) *</label>
                <select id="rating" name="rating" class="form-control" required>
                    <option value="">Select Rating</option>
                    <option value="1">1 - Very Bad</option>
                    <option value="2">2 - Bad</option>
                    <option value="3">3 - Average</option>
                    <option value="4">4 - Good</option>
                    <option value="5">5 - Excellent</option>
                </select>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group logo-upload">
                <input type="file" id="screenshot" name="screenshot" class="file-input" accept="image/*">
                <label for="screenshot" class="file-label">Choose File</label>
                <small>Optional: Attach a screenshot related to your feedback or complaint.</small>
            </div>

            <div class="form-group submit-button">
                <button type="submit" class="submit-btn">Submit Feedback</button>
            </div>
        </form>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
